      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The health workers' union conducted a\u00a0 protest in front of the National Hospital, appealing to the government to stop the repression immediately, not to cut health staff allowances and to\u00a0 insider allowing concessions. Pix by Nimalsiri Edirisinghe."
      ],
